 The percentage of the national assessment that has been allocated
to each class of tobacco product and the total amount of assessments
due from each such class;

 Any adjustments that have been from the prior fiscal year with
respect to the allocation of the gross domestic volume determined
for use in a fiscal year among the classes of tobacco products;

 Quota transferred by lease or by owner, for all kinds of tobacco
except flue-cured and cigar tobacco; except for flue-cured disaster
