contents.P:

  Tobacco

 means the following kinds of tobacco: Burley tobacco (type 31);
cigar-filler and cigar binder tobacco (types 42, 43, 44, 53, 54, and
55); dark air-cured tobacco (types 35 and 36), fire-cured tobacco
(types 21, 22 and 23); flue-cured tobacco (types 11, 12, 13 and 14);
and Virginia sun-cured tobacco (type 37).

